#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag1.58:4.1"
msgid "1.58. Ramaṇīyakuṭikattheragāthā"
msgstr "1.58. Ramaṇīyakuṭika"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="vns" id="vns58"></a><a class="vnp" id="vnp58"></a>
msgctxt "thag1.58:5.1"
msgid "“Ramaṇīyā me kuṭikā,"
msgstr "My little hut is pleasing, delightful,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.58:5.2"
msgid "Saddhādeyyā manoramā;"
msgstr "a gift given in faith."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.58:5.3"
msgid "Na me attho kumārīhi,"
msgstr "I’ve no need of girls:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.58:5.4"
msgid "Yesaṃ attho tahiṃ gacchatha nāriyo”ti."
msgstr "go, ladies, to those in need!"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
